Package: ggpicrust2
Type: Package
Title: Make 'PICRUSt2' Output Analysis and Visualization Easier
Version: 1.4.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chen", "Yang", email = "cafferychen7850@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Liangliang", "Zhang", email = "lxz716@case.edu ", role = "aut"))
Description: The 'ggpicrust2' package makes it easy to analyze and visualize 'PICRUSt2' output. 
    It offers pre-defined plots and functions to generate statistical plots about microbiome functional predictions, as well as customization options. 
    Plus, with its one-click feature to generate publication-level plots, you can save time and create professional-grade figures with ease. 
    Try the 'ggpicrust2' package to streamline your 'PICRUSt2' analysis and visualization process.
